title: The David Fincher Rankings, Part I
description:
It's Fincher Week at The Ringer, so Sean and Amanda are teaming up with Chris Ryan to present a highly sophisticated, meticulous ranking of the filmmaker's work that would make Fincher proud. In Part I, they analyze his feature films, TV series, commercials, and music videos and build a hierarchy of the top 25 Fincher works.

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Guest: Chris Ryan
